org.xchain.annotations

Annotation Type In


  • @Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Inherited
@Documented
public @interface In
    Specifies that a field or a setter method is to be injected with a value from the context.
    Author:
    Devon Tackett
